      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 33 九三</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 33 九三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九三：系遯，有疾厲，畜臣妾吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third NINE, undivided, shows one retiring but bound,--to his distress and peril. (If he were to deal with his binders as in) nourishing a servant or concubine, it would be fortunate for him.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
