      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 33 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五：嘉遯，貞吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows its subject retiring in an admirable way. With firm correctness there will be good fortune.</seg>
